The paper focuses on the intersection of active learning and explainable AI, with a particular emphasis on the human experience of annotators. This suggests that the paper is likely to be categorized under Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses natural language processing (NLP) tasks, which suggests a potential categorization under Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) or Information Retrieval (cs.IR).
